Q: Fleet information of Air 7 LLC？
SQL: SELECT aircraft_details.aircraft_model_name FROM aircraft_details JOIN supplier_details ON aircraft_details.supplier_id = supplier_details.supplier_id WHERE supplier_details.supplier_name = "Air 7 LLC";
actual_SQL:
SELECT ad.aircraft_id,
       ad.aircraft_model_name,
       ad.type_code,
       ad.brand_name,
       ad.aircraft_length,
       ad.aircraft_width,
       ad.aircraft_height,
       ad.cabin_length,
       ad.cabin_width,
       ad.cabin_height,
       ad.max_range,
       ad.cruise_speed,
       ad.registration,
       ad.make_year,
       ad.seat_num,
       ad.aircraft_base,
       ad.status,
       ad.aircraft_amenity_type
FROM aircraft_details ad
WHERE ad.supplier_id IN
    (SELECT sd.supplier_id
     FROM supplier_details sd
     WHERE sd.supplier_name IN ('Advanced Air LLC',
                                'Air 7 LLC',
                                'Air Business LLC',
                                'Air Direct LLC',
                                'Cobalt Air LLC',
                                'Direct2 Air LLC',
                                'Katmai Air LLC',
                                'Regency Air LLC',
                                'Tailwind Air LLC',
                                'Talon Air LLC',
                                'Triton Air LLC',
                                'Valkyrie Air LLC'))
LIMIT 50;
